Method
- Fungsi yang bekerja dalam object
- Non-OOP: "functions"; OOP:"methods"
- Didefinisikan seperti fungsi biasa di dalam class

class Person
{
    var $first_name;
    var $country = 'None';

    function sayHello()
    {
        return "Hello, World!"
    }
}

$customer = new Person;

$customer->first_name = "Rafi";

echo $customer->first_name;
// Rafi

echo $customer->sayHello();
// Hello, World!